No response when changing to the next set of remote control codes: When clicking the switch button, the air conditioner has no response.
There is no response when changing to the next set of remote control codes: When clicking the Temperature + button, the air conditioner does not respond at all.
There is no response when changing to the next set of remote control codes: When clicking the Temperature- button, the air conditioner does not respond at all.
There is no response when changing to the next set of remote control codes: When clicking the Mode button, the air conditioner does not respond at all.
The key matching is successful and responsive: when you click the switch button, you can turn on or off the air conditioner
The button matching is successful and responsive: when you click the Temperature + button, you can adjust the air conditioner temperature to increase.
The button matching is successful and responsive: when you click the Temperature- button, you can adjust the air conditioner temperature to lower
The button matching is successful and responsive: when you click the Mode button, you can adjust the mode options of the air conditioner normally.
There is no response when changing to the next set of remote control codes: When clicking the Power button, the TV does not respond at all.
There is no response when changing to the next set of remote control codes: When clicking the Mute button, the TV volume does not respond at all.
There is no response when changing to the next set of remote control codes: When clicking the Volume button, the TV volume does not respond at all.
The key matching is successful and responsive: when you click the Power button, you can turn the TV on or off
The key matching is successful and responsive: when you click the Mute button, you can control the volume of the TV to turn off or on
The key matching is successful and responsive: when you click the Volume button, you can adjust the volume of the TV
